    "notes": "mūla śrīgurvvaṣṭaka: śrīviśvanātha cakravartti-ṭhākura",
    "verses": "\ndābānala-sama saṁsāra-dahane \ndagdha-jībakula-uddhāra kāraṇe |\nkaruṇā-bārida kṛpābāri-dāne \n(bandi) guṇasindhu gurura caraṇa-kamala ||1||\n\nnṛtya-gīta-bādya-śrīharikīrttane\nrahenô magana mahāmatta mane |\nromāñca kampāśru haya gaurapreme \nbandi sei gurura caraṇa-kamala ||2||\n\nsadā rata ĵini bigraha-sebane\nśṛṅgārādi āra mandira-mārjjane |\nkarena niĵukta anugatajane \nbandi sei gurura caraṇa-kamala ||3||\n\ncarbbya-cuṣya-lehya-peya-rasamaya\nprasādānna kṛṣṇera ati svādu haya |\nbhakta-āsvādane nija tṛpta raya\nbandi sei gurura caraṇa-kamala ||4||\n\nśrīrādhāmādhava-nāma-rūpa-guṇe\nananta mādhurĵya-līlā-āsvādane |\nlubdha citta ĵini hana pratikṣaṇe\nbandi sei gurura caraṇa-kamala ||5||\n\nvrajaĵubadvandva-rati-sambarddhane\nĵukti kare sakhīgaṇe vṛndāvane, |\nati dakṣa tāhe, priyatamagaṇe \nbandi sei gurura caraṇa-kamala ||6||\n\nsarbbaśāstre gāya śrīharira svarūpa\nbhaktagaṇa bhābe sei anurūpa, |\nkintu ĵini prabhu-priyatama-rūpa\nbandi sei gurura caraṇa-kamala ||7||\n\nĵā̃hāra prasāde kṛṣṇakṛpā pāi\nĵā̃’ra aprasāde anya gati nāi |\ntri-sandhyā kīrttira staba dhyāne bhāi\nbandi sei gurura caraṇa-kamala ||8||\n\ngurudevāṣṭaka ati ĵatnakôri’\nbrāhma-muhūrtte paḓe ucca kôri’ |\nvṛndāvana-nātha sākṣāt. śrīhari\nsebā pāya sei bastusiddhi-kāle ||9||"
