    "author": "vaiṣṇava dāsa",
    "verses": "\njayare jayare jaya,    paramahaṁsa mahāśaya,\nśrībhaktisiddhānta sarasvatī |\ngosvāmī ṭhākura jaya,    parama karuṇāmaya,\ndīna-hīna agatira gati ||1||\n\nnīlācale hô_iyā udaya |\nśrīgauḓamaṇḍale āsi’,    premabhakti parakāśi’,\njībera nāśilā bhaba-bhaya ||2||\n\ntomāra mahimā gāi,    henô sādhya mora nāi,\ntabe pāri, ĵadi dehô’ śakti |\nbiśvahite abirata,    ācāra-pracāre rata,\nbiśuddhā śrīrūpānugā bhakti ||3||\n\nśrīpāṭa khetari dhāma,    ṭhākura śrīnarottama,\ntomāte tā̃hāra guṇa dekhi |\nśāstrera siddhānta-sāra,    śuni’ lāge camat.kāra,\nkutārkika dite nāre phā̃ki ||4||\n\nśuddhabhakti-mata ĵatô,    upadharmma-kabalita,\nheriyā lokera mane trāsa |\nhāni’ susiddhānta-bāṇa,    upadharmma khāna khāna,\nsajjanera bāḓā’le ullāsa ||5||\n\nsmārttamata-jaladhara,    śuddhabhakti-rabi-kara,\nācchādilô bhābiyā antare |\nśāstrasindhu-manthanete,    susiddhānta-jhañjhābāte,\nuḓāilā dig_#digantare ||6||\n\nsthāne sthāne katô maṭha,    sthāpiyāchô niṣkapaṭa,\npremasebā śikhāite jībe |\nmaṭhera vaiṣṇavagaṇa,    kare sadā bitaraṇa,\nhariguṇa-kathāmṛta bhabe ||7||\n\nśuddhabhakti-mandākinī,    bimala prabāhô āni’,\nśītala kôrilô taptaprāṇa |\ndeśe deśe niṣkiñcana,    prerilā vaiṣṇavagaṇa,\nbistārite hariguṇagāna ||8||\n\npūrbbe ĵathā gaurahari,    māyāvāda cheda kôri’,\nvaiṣṇava kôrilā kāśīvāsī |\nvaiṣṇavadarśana-sūkṣma,    bicāre tumi he dakṣa,\ntemati toṣilā vārāṇasī ||9||\n\ndaibabarṇāśrama-dharmma,    haribhakti ĵāra marmma \nśāstraĵuktye kôrilā niścaya |\njñāna-ĵoga-karmmacaya,    mūlya tāra kichu naya,\nbhaktira birodhī ĵadi haya ||10||\n\nśrīgauḓamaṇḍala bhūmi,    bhaktasaṅge parikrami’,\nsukīrtti sthāpilā mahāśaya |\nabhinna vrajamaṇḍala,    gauḓabhūmi premojjvala,\npracāra hô_ilô viśvamaya ||11||\n\nkuliyāte pāṣaṇḍīrā,    atyācāra kailô ĵā’rā,\ntā-sabāra doṣa kṣamā kôri’ |\njagate kaile ghoṣaṇā,    ‘taroriva sahiṣṇunā’,\nhana ‘kīrttanīyaḥ sadā hariḥ’ ||12||\n\nśrīviśvavaiṣṇava-rāja,    sabhāmadhye “pātrarāja”,\nupādhi-bhūṣaṇe bibhūṣita |\nviśvera maṅgala lāgi’,    hô_iyāchô sarbbatyāgī,\nbiśvābāsijana-hite rata ||13||\n\nkôritechô upakāra,    ĵā’te para-upakāra,\nlabhe jība śrīkṛṣṇa-sebāya |\ndūre ĵāya bhaba-roga,    khaṇḍe ĵāhe karmmabhoga,\nharipādapadma ĵā’te pāya ||14||\n\njība moha-nidrāgata,    jāgā’te vaikuṇṭhadūta,\n‘gauḓīya’ pāṭhāo ghare ghare | \nuṭhôre uṭhôre bhāi,    āra tô’ samaya nāi,\n‘kṛṣṇa bhajô’ bôlô uccaiḥsvare ||15||\n\ntomāra mukhārabinda-,    bigalita makaranda,\nsiñcita acyuta-guṇagāthā |\nśunile juḓāya prāṇa,    tamo-moha antarddhāna,\ndūre ĵāya hṛdayera byathā ||16||\n\njāni āmi mahāśaya,    ĵaśobāñchā nāhi haya,\nbindumātra tomāra antare |\ntaba guṇa bīṇādhārī,    mora kaṇṭha-bīṇā dhôri’,\nabaśeṣe bôlāya āmāre ||17||\n\nvaiṣṇavera guṇa-gāna,    kôrile jībera trāṇa,\nśuniyāchi sādhu-guru-mukhe |\nkṛṣṇabhakti samudaya,    janama saphala haya,\ne bhaba-sāgara tare sukhe ||18||\n\nte kāraṇe e prayāsa,    ĵathā bāmanera āśa,\ngaganera cā̃da dhôribāre |\nadoṣa-daraśī tumi,    adhama patita āmi,\nnijaguṇe kṣamibā āmāre ||19||\n\nśrīgaurāṅga-pāriṣada,    ṭhākura-bhaktivinoda,\ndīna-hīna patitera bandhu |\nkalitama-bināśite,    ānilena abanīte,\ntomā’ akalaṅka pūrṇa indu ||20||\n\nkarô kṛpā bitaraṇa,    premasudhā anukṣaṇa,\nmātiyā uṭhuka jībagaṇa |\nharināma-saṅkīrttane,    nācuka jagata-jane,\nvaiṣṇava-dāsera nibedana ||21||"
