    "title": "jaya gadādharābhinna bhakativinoda",
    "author": "lekhaka ajānā",
    "verses": "\njaya gadādharābhinna bhakativinoda |\ncidānandamaya tanu bhaktaprāṇāmoda ||1||\n\nuddhāra kôrile lupta tīrtha-māyāpura |\njaya-nāmācārĵya bhaktivinoda ṭhākura ||2||\n\nsvānanda-sukhada-kuñja, rādhākuṇḍa-tīra |\nbiśuddha bhajana-sthāna—samādhi-mandira ||3||\n\njaya jaya nīlācala śrībhakti-kuṭīra |\nśrībhaktivinoda-sthāna samudrera tīra ||4||\n\njaya jaya śrīkalyāṇa-kalpatarurāja |\nṭhākura ānilô ĵā̃hā dharaṇīra mājha ||5||\n\nśrībhakti-bhabana jaya giridhara-sthāna |\njaya tirobhāba-tithi bhaktagaṇa-prāṇa ||6||\n\njaya gaura-pādapadma-rasa-madhukara |\nnāma-rase bhāsāilā jībera antara ||7||\n\njaya upadeśāmṛta madhura mūrati |\njānāilā jībagaṇe nāmera śakati ||8||\n\nbhakativinoda prabhu gaura-nija-jana |\nharināma-mahāmantra ĵā̃hāra sādhana ||9||\n\nsei se vinoda-pada bharasā ĵā̃hāra |\njaya guṇagāna gāhe adhama se chāra ||10||\n\ndayā kôri’ śrīcaraṇa-sebā adhikāra |\ndio deva! ihā chāḓā āśā nāhi āra ||11||"
