    "author": "śrīla bhaktivinoda ṭhākura",
    "verses": "\nore mana, bhukti-mukti-spṛhā karô’ dūra |\nbhogera nāhikô śeṣa,    tāhe nāhi sukhaleśa,\nnirānanda tāhāte pracura ||1||\n\nindriya-tarpaṇa bô_i,    bhoge āra sukha kô_i,\nseo sukha abhāba-pūraṇa |\nĵe-sukhete āche bhaya,    tāke sukha balā naya,\ntāke duḥkha bôle bijña-jana ||2||\n\nśāstre phalaśruti ĵatô,    sei lobhe katôśata,\nmūḓhajana bhoga-prati dhāya |\nse-saba kaitaba jāni’,    chāḓiyā vaiṣṇava-jñānī,\nmukhyaphala kṛṣṇarati pāya ||3||\n\nmukti-bāñchā duṣṭa ati,    naṣṭa kare śiṣṭamati,\nmuktispṛhā kaitaba-pradhāna |\ntāhā ĵe chāḓite nāre,    māyā nāhi chāḓe tāre,\ntāra ĵatna nahe phalabān_ ||4||\n\nataeba spṛhādvaya,    chāḓi’ śodhô’ e hṛdaya,\nnāhi rākhô kāmera bāsanā |\nbhoga-mokṣa nāhi cāi,    śrīkṛṣṇacaraṇa pāi,\nvinodera ei tô sādhanā ||5||",
