    "author": "manoharadāsa",
    "verses": "\njaya jaya pãhu śrīla sanātana nāma | \nsakala bhubana māhā ĵachu guṇagrāma ||1||\n\ntejala sakala sukha sampad_ apāra | \nśrīcaitanya caraṇa-ĵugala karu sāra ||2||\n\nśrīvṛndāvana-bhūme kôri’ bāsa | \nlupata tīrtha saba karalô prakāśa ||3||\n\nśrīgovinda-sebā paracāri’ | \nkaralô bhāgavata-artha bicāri’ ||4||\n\nĵugala-bhajana, līlā-guṇa-nāma | \nkaralô bithāra grantha anupama ||5||\n\nsatata gaurapreme garagara dehõ | \nbhrama_i vṛndāvane nā pāya_i thehô ||6||\n\nbipula pulakabhara nayanahi nīra | \n‘rāi kānu’ bôli’ paḓa_i athira ||7||\n\nbhāba-bibhūṣaṇa sakala śarīra | \nanukhana bihara_i ĵamunāka tīra ||8||\n\nĵachu karuṇāmaya vṛndāvana pāi | \nbhāba_i manohara soi gosāñi ||9||"
