    "notes": "(śrīpremavivartta)",
    "verses": "\nasādhu-saṅge bhāi, kṛṣṇanāma nāhi haya |\nnāmākṣara bāhirāya baṭe, tabu nāma kabhu naya ||1||\n\nkabhu nāmābhāsa haya, sadā nāma-aparādha |\nesaba jānibe bhāi kṛṣṇabhaktira bādha ||2||\n\nĵadi kôribe kṛṣṇanāma, sādhusaṅga karô |\nbhukti-mukti-siddhibāñchā dūre parihara ||3||\n\n‘daśa aparādha’ tyajô, māna-apamāna |\nanāsaktye biṣaya bhuñja, āra lahô kṛṣṇanāma ||4||\n\nkṛṣṇabhaktira anukūla-saba karahô svīkāra |\nkṛṣṇabhaktira pratikūla-saba karô parihāra ||5||\n\njñāna-ĵoga-ceṣṭā chāḓô, āra karmmasaṅga |\nmarkaṭa-bairāgya tyajô, ĵāte deharaṅga ||6||\n\n‘kṛṣṇa āmāya pāle, rākhe’, jānô sarbbakāla |\nātmanibedana-dainye ghucāo jañjāla ||7||\n\nsādhu pāoŵā kaṣṭa baḓô jībera jāniyā |\nsādhu-bhaktarūpe kṛṣṇa āilô nadīyā ||8||\n\ngorāpada āśraya karahô buddhimān_ |\ngorā bô_i sādhu-guru āche kebā ān_ ||9||"
